'''Green Wiki''' is a wiki site about [[sustainability]]. It is one of a number of '''[[green wikis]]''', which also include [[Appropedia]]. It is licensed under the same [[open license]] as Appropedia and Wikipedia ([[CC-by-sa]]).

It is commercially operated by Wikia and has advertising. Its focus is on [[green living]].

It was formerly called '''Wikia Green'''.

